==人口==
根据2000年人口统计，迈阿密海滩人口为87,933人，[[人口密度|人口密度]]为4,829.5/km<sup>2</sup>。白人占86.74%（40.9%为非拉美裔白人）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.muninetguide.com/states/florida/municipality/Miami_Beach.php |title=Demographics of Miami Beach, Fla. |publisher=MuniNetGuide.com |accessdate=2007-11-01 |archive-date=2010-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205201924/http://www.muninetguide.com/states/florida/municipality/Miami_Beach.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>、黑人占4.03%、印第安人占0.23%、亚裔占1.37%。各种族的拉美裔人口占53.45%。

